Check dimensions

Source: R/checkers.R
check_dimensions.Rd

An internal function used within apply_vaccination() to warn users of incompatible dimensions of data and the next generation matrices

Usage

check_dimensions(ngm, data)

Arguments

ngm

list with next generation matrices at different settings

data

data frame
